description: Bergio International, Inc. designs, manufactures, and distributes fine jewelry primarily in the United States. It offers a range of products made from precious metals, such as gold, platinum, and Karat gold, as well as diamonds and other precious stones. The company provides upscale jewelry comprising white diamonds, yellow diamonds, pearls, and palladium, as well as colored stones in 18K gold and platinum. In addition, it offers handbags, and couture line, bridal line, and other of kind pieces. Further, the company operates two retail stores. The company offers its products under the Bergio brand name. Bergio International, Inc. is headquartered in Fairfield, New Jersey.
